   377в†’## Caveats
   382в†’By default, `input-otp` handles password managers for you.
   383в†’The password manager badges should be automatically shifted to the right side.
   384в†’
   385в†’However, if you still want to block password managers, please disable the `pushPasswordManagerStrategy` and then manually block each PWM.
   386в†’
   387в†’```diff
   388в†’<OTPInput
